
For a normal autotools installs run:

	./configure --prefix=/the/dir/you/want/the/installation
	make
	make install

Executable will be in:
	/the/dir/you/want/the/installation/bin/ben-jose-solver

Library will be in:
	/the/dir/you/want/the/installation/lib/libben-jose.a

For help run:

	./configure --help 

All documentation in '<base_dir>/doc'.

